    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK">Index XXXII.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XXXI.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XXXI. de <app>
                                <rdg wit="#S1 #S2">Muhamete</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#S3">Mahumete</rdg>
                            </app> ab obsidione castelli Iaicza depulso</rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿Paucis post <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">haec</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M"/>
                    </app> diebus quieti datis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #M">coepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">caepit</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">cepit</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                    </app> suas omnes cogitationes ad ea convertere, quibus omnes cum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praeteritarum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">preteritarum</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S3 #M">discordiarum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2">difcordiarum</rdg>
                    </app> tum futurorum dissidiorum causae ex universo regno tollerentur.</s>
                <s n="2">Quare comparatis undique copiis cogit exercitum, qui tantus fuit, ut <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2">esset et</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">esset</rdg>
                    </app> securitati subiectis et adversantibus formidini.</s>
                <s n="3">Praesidia deinde valida collocat in locis, quibus maior est visa
                    necessitas, in regni praesertim finibus, ut, si quid hostile ingrueret, obviam
                    illi iretur facilius.</s>
                <s n="4">Curat <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praeterea</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">preterea</rdg>
                    </app>, ut, si quid in Hungaria turbatum esset propter et regni mutationem et
                    novitatem rerum, reducatur in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">tranquillitatem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #M">tranquilitatem</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="5">Ita ordinatis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Hungariae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Hungarie</rdg>
                    </app> rebus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">nuntiatur</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2">nunciatur</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Mathie</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthiae</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">Mahamettum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #M">Mahammetum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Mahumetum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2">Muhametem</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">Mahumetem</rdg>
                    </app> Turcarum imperatorem cum magno bellicarum omnis generis rerum apparatu
                    venisse in Bosnam, quae regio <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">est portio</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">portio est</rdg>
                    </app> quaedam montanae Dalmatiae, cuius habitatores colunt Christum iuxta
                    orientalis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ecclesiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">ecclesie</rdg>
                    </app> ritum.</s>
                <s n="6">Nec multo post fama ad <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Mathie</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthiae</rdg>
                    </app> pervenit aures illum circumsedisse <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #M">Iaizzam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Iayzzam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Iaiczam</rdg>
                    </app>, quod castellum in eo regno est <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">et loci</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">loci</rdg>
                    </app> natura et muri cum altitudine tum latitudine munitissimum.</s>
                <s n="7">Cumque esset ipsius <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2 #S3 #M">Mathiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Mathie</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2">Matthiae</rdg>
                    </app> ditionis, nihil ulterius <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">protelandum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">praestolandum</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ipse</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2"/>
                    </app> ratus ita, ut erat valide instructus, copias ducit in Bosnam adversus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R">Mahammettum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Mahumetum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2">Muhametem</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">Mahumetem</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#M">Mahammetum</rdg>
                    </app> belli <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">pugnaeque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">pugneque</rdg>
                    </app> fortunam tentaturus.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">5–7 = Th
                        4.65.</note></s>
                <s n="8">Eius rei ut ille per exploratores certior est factus, sentiens <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praeterea</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">preterea</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthiae</rdg>
                    </app> exercitum esse et iuventute florentem et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #M">armis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3">annis</rdg>
                    </app> roboreque militum ac tormentorum vi magna validissimum, ratus non esse
                    tutum cum instructissimo hoste confligere, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">perterritus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">perteritus</rdg>
                    </app> castra <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">movere</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #L1 #L2">moveri</rdg>
                    </app>, suosque omnes e loco discedere, eoque, unde venerant, redire iussit.</s>
                <s n="9">Quare effectum est, ut ob repentinam fugam compulsus sit ibidem bellicas
                    omnes machinas <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">aeneaque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">eneasque</rdg>
                    </app> tormenta in hostis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">potestatem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">potestate</rdg>
                    </app> relinquere.</s>
                <s n="10">Pro cuius <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">victoriae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">victorie</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">felici</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R">foelici</rdg>
                    </app> eventu <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                    </app> egit immortali deo gratias, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #M">coepitque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">caepitque</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">cepitque</rdg>
                    </app> inde sperare fortunam divino favore <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S3 #M">ceteris</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2">caeteris</rdg>
                    </app> in posterum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S3 #M">gerendis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2">gerentis</rdg>
                    </app> a se rebus semper aspiraturam.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">8–10 = Th
                        4.66.</note></s>
            </p>
            </div>
